description:
(I'm also using mongoid if that helps but I don't think it's related)

I call MongoidClass.collection.aggregate(<query>).explain

Applicable Stack Trace:
{noformat}6: from /Users/me/.rvm/gems/ruby-2.5.1/gems/mongo-2.3.1/lib/mongo/collection/view/aggregation.rb:88:in `explain'
 5: from /Users/me/.rvm/gems/ruby-2.5.1/gems/mongo-2.3.1/lib/mongo/collection/view/aggregation.rb:88:in `first'
 4: from /Users/me/.rvm/gems/ruby-2.5.1/gems/mongo-2.3.1/lib/mongo/collection/view/iterable.rb:44:in `each'
 3: from /Users/me/.rvm/gems/ruby-2.5.1/gems/mongo-2.3.1/lib/mongo/cursor.rb:110:in `each'
